[edit]



This is a list of all current Wikimedia Foundation projects. Please note that this is not a list of sites using the MediaWiki software.


There is an overview of large Wikimedia projects and a List of Wikipedias

For a tabular view of projects, see Table of Wikimedia projects (by size), or the automatically updated  Special:SiteMatrix

For proposed projects, see Category:Proposed projects and Proposals for new projects

To download a copy of a project, see download.wikimedia.org

For a complete list of mailing lists, IRC and other channels, see List of communications channels

[edit]

This is a list of all current Wikimedia Foundation projects. Please note that this is not a list of sites using the MediaWiki software.

  • There is an overview of large Wikimedia projects and a List of Wikipedias
  • For a tabular view of projects, see Table of Wikimedia projects (by size), or the automatically updated Special:SiteMatrix
  • For proposed projects, see Category:Proposed projects and Proposals for new projects
  • To download a copy of a project, see download.wikimedia.org
  • For a complete list of mailing lists, IRC and other channels, see List of communications channels

Project pages on MetaWiki:
Wikimedia • Meta • MediaWiki • Wikimedia Commons • Wikipedia • Wiktionary • Wikinews • Wikiquote • Wikibooks • Wikiversity • Wikisource • Wikivoyage • Wikijunior • Wikispecies • Incubator • Sep11wiki

See also: the Nostalgia wiki (ca 2001), MediaWiki settings of Wikimedia projects, Wikimedia wikis (where also non-project wikis are listed).

Wikimedia coordination and other projects[edit]

Many of these are multilingual sites (at least nominally), but none have language sub-projects.

Wikimedia Foundation sites:

Foundation wikis: Wikimedia Foundation (restricted editing) • Wikimedia Foundation Office (private) • Wikimedia Board of Trustees (private) • Wikimedia chapters & foundation (private, defunct) • Wikimedia contractor collaborations (private) • Wikimedia Advisory Board (defunct, merging into meta)

Committees: Affiliations committee (private) • Special Projects committee (private, defunct) • Grants wiki (private, defunct)

Wikimedia community sites:

Meta-Wiki • Wikimedia strategic planning (read-only) • Wikimedia Incubator • Nostalgia wiki (read-only) • Outreach wiki • Wikipedia 10th anniversary planning (read-only) • Wikimedia Usability wiki (read-only)
